{"tid":506986,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果意圖令 IPhone 性能下降 料引發集體訴訟","createTime":"2017-12-22T18:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T09:22:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"22d60c20202d2e6e4d60a6432f72baf6a9edc833","tid":506986,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:02:22.000Z","msg":"Lawton<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n早前蘋果承認由於要避免 iPhone 因電池老化而突然出現自行關機配象，有意圖地令 iPhone 性能下降。而事件有進一步發展。美國有用戶在網上發起呼籲，招集用戶對蘋果進行集體訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事件的起因是有人在網上發表了兩個主機性能跑分數據，在更換電池後，主機跑分數字大幅提升，表示原本的性能是有被強制減低的可能性。而蘋果在 20 日發聲明承認有關做法，指電池在低溫操作時會減低壽命，另外在老化的情況下，容易出現自動關機的情況，因此在 iOS 加入在特定情況下降低處理器效能的「功能」。<br />\n<br />\n今次準備提訴的是居住於洛杉磯的 iPhone 用戶 Stefan Bodganovich 以及 Dakota Speas。根據網媒《TMZ》報道，Bodganovich 是 iPhone 7 的使用者。<br />\n<br />\n根據 Bodganovich 的指控，蘋果引入了限制主機性能的措施，令 iPhone 用戶擁有的 iPhone 價值受損，並且並非用戶本身的希望，這個決定也沒有得到用戶的同意。還有他主張「蘋果是令用保護劣化電池為籍口，意圖令用戶購買新機」。蘋果在新款 iPhone 發售時意圖令舊 iPhone 的性能下降，而沒有將所有事實適切地展示，破壞了蘋果與 iPhone 用戶之間隱然的契約。Bodganovich 要求蘋果對此作出賠償，並停止對舊機進行性能上的限制，他呼籲 iPhone 7／7 Plus 或以前的 iPhone 擁有者參與他的集團訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：The Mercury News<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=Iy0naNJY9kzon15L2DFTHJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=8a183ba5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁<a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=Iy0naNJY9kzon15L2DFTHJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=1c162eb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a><br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=Iy0naNJY9kzon15L2DFTHJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=6f851742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關文章<br />\n蘋果承認舊 iPhone 「有意」降速　劣電 iPhone 6 / 6S / 7 /SE 受影響 - <a href=\"http://UNWIRE.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUNWIRE.HK&d=Iy0naNJY9kzon15L2DFTHJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=bb4815c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">UNWIRE.HK</a><br />\n傳蘋果計劃在明年開始合併 iPhone 與 Mac Apps - <a href=\"http://UNWIRE.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUNWIRE.HK&d=Iy0naNJY9kzon15L2DFTHJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=bb4815c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">UNWIRE.HK</a><br />\n蘋果 iPhone X 腮紅金版傳明年農曆新年推出 - <a href=\"http://UNWIRE.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUNWIRE.HK&d=Iy0naNJY9kzon15L2DFTHJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=bb4815c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">UNWIRE.HK</a><br />\n<br />\n前一篇文章<br />\n手機影聖誕燈飾 + 人像 必學 5 招<br />\n下一篇文章<br />\n蘋果要求 : 遊戲「抽蛋」必須提供中獎比率資料<br />\n返回頂部<br />\nFocus RetrieverFacebookWhatsAppLineGoogle+Email"},{"pid":"2ed900a3952880e782ba036c457979428fd28b17","tid":506986,"uid":127988,"like":2,"dislike":56,"score":-54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:03:25.000Z","msg":"沒錢唔好學心用iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adffe6624438e77589d3157185685135fd84a16c","tid":506986,"uid":45914,"like":87,"dislike":2,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:04:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1035f8cde83adacc598d168938e13cf37a75c55","tid":506986,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"用唉瘋想唔有新用最新？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77ba1509c7a27690ebba1e8b62146c2d2fef695","tid":506986,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaeb923b626904fe3707cfc914c1d1d0fcbbd7b9","tid":506986,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:21:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a625e